<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Product Details</title>
    <!-- Bootstrap 5 CSS -->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap-icons@1.10.5/font/bootstrap-icons.css">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background-color: #7e8a9870;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            padding: 0 15px;
        }

        .product-card {
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 20px;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .product-card h1 {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #2c3e50;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .product-content {
            display: flex;
            gap: 30px;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .product-image {
            flex: 1;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .product-image img {
            max-width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .product-image img:hover {
            transform: scale(1.05);
        }

        .product-image p {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin: 10px 0;
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-top: 10px;
        }

        .gallery img {
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .gallery img:hover {
            opacity: 0.7;
        }

        .product-details {
            flex: 1;
            min-width: 300px;
        }

        .price {
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .discount {
            color: #e74c3c;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            text-decoration: line-through;
            margin-right: 10px;
        }

        .current-price {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: 700;
        }

        .availability {
            color: #27ae60;
            font-weight: 500;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .description-note {
            color: #7f8c8d;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }

        .buy-options {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .buy-options button {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .buy-now {
            background-color: #3498db;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .buy-now:hover {
            background-color: #2980b9;
        }

        .add-to-cart {
            background-color: #2ecc71;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .add-to-cart:hover {
            background-color: #27ae60;
        }

        .add-to-wishlist {
            background-color: #e67e22;
            color: #fff;
        }

        .add-to-wishlist:hover {
            background-color: #d35400;
        }

        .color-options {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .color-options label {
            margin-right: 15px;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .color-options input[type="radio"] {
            margin-right: 5px;
        }

        .additional-info {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            color: #7f8c8d;
        }

        .additional-info li {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .additional-info span {
            margin-right: 10px;
            color: #3498db;
        }

        .product-tabs {
            display: flex;
            gap: 10px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #ecf0f1;
        }

        .tab {
            padding: 10px 20px;
            border: none;
            background: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #7f8c8d;
            transition: color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .tab.active {
            color: #2c3e50;
            border-bottom: 2px solid #3498db;
        }

        .tab:hover {
            color: #2980b9;
        }

        .tab-content {
            display: none;
            padding-top: 20px;
            color: #34495e;
        }

        .tab-content.active {
            display: block;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .product-content {
                flex-direction: column;
                text-align: center;
            }

            .product-image {
                margin-bottom: 20px;
            }

            .buy-options {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .buy-options button {
                width: 100%;
            }

            .product-card h1 {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .current-price {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="product-card">
            <h1>Swarm White Purple Wireless Gaming Keyboard</h1>
            <div class="product-content">
                <div class="product-image">
                    <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="Swarm Keyboard">
                    <p>75% KEYS LAYOUT</p>
                    <div class="gallery">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50x50" alt="Thumbnail 1">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50x50" alt="Thumbnail 2">
                        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/50x50" alt="Thumbnail 3">
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="product-details">
                    <div class="price">
                        <span class="discount">42% off $579.00</span>
                        <span class="current-price">$129.00</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="availability">In Stock</p>
                    <p class="description-note">This is a beautiful & 3D printed keyboard, which makes typing so much fun and will be available all over India.</p>
                    <div class="buy-options">
                        <button class="buy-now">BUY NOW</button>
                        <button class="add-to-cart">Add to cart</button>
                        <button class="add-to-wishlist">Add to wishlist</button>
                    </div>
                    <div class="color-options">
                        <label><input type="radio" name="color" value="purple" checked> Purple</label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="color" value="black"> Black</label>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="additional-info">
                        <li><span>üöö</span> Free Delivery apply to all orders above $500</li>
                        <li><span>üõ°Ô∏è</span> We assure a safe delivery with extra protection fee of $29</li>
                        <li><span>üîÑ</span> 1 day return/replacement date for the products from delivery date</li>
                        <li><span>üì¶</span> Delivery all over India within a week express delivery.</li>
                        <li><span>üîß</span> Warranty for the products for one year for this product</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="product-tabs">
                <button class="tab active" data-tab="description">Description</button>
                <button class="tab" data-tab="specifications">Specifications</button>
                <button class="tab" data-tab="reviews">Reviews</button>
            </div>
            <div class="tab-content active" id="description">
                <p>A gasket-mounted keyboard enhances typing by using a flexible gasket between the plate and case, which softens keystrokes and reduces vibrations. This design provides a quieter, more comfortable experience, ideal for long sessions, while also improving key consistency and overall smoothness.</p>
                <p>With Swarm's 4000mAh battery, game on for 270 with all lights off. At full brightness with all lights on Swarm offers a battery life of 20 hours.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Tab switching functionality
        document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(tab => {
            tab.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const tabs = document.querySelectorAll('.tab');
                const tabContents = document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content');

                tabs.forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
                tab.classList.add('active');

                tabContents.forEach(content => content.classList.remove('active'));
                document.getElementById(tab.dataset.tab).classList.add('active');
            });
        });

        // Thumbnail gallery functionality (optional, if needed)
        document.querySelectorAll('.gallery img').forEach(thumbnail => {
            thumbnail.addEventListener('click', () => {
                const mainImage = document.querySelector('.product-image img');
                mainImage.src = thumbnail.src;
            });
        });
    </script>
</body>
</html>